meanings.sent2: The company's overcompliances with safety protocols ensured a secure work environment.
meanings.sent3: His overcompliances with the traffic rules became a running joke among his friends.
meanings.sent4: The overcompliances of the robot with its programming made it seem almost human.
meanings.sent5: The overcompliances of the student with the assignment guidelines impressed the teacher.
